synatx:
  mkdir  [directorys/folders]

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

mkdir directoryname  :create directory
mkdir -p new/img  : will create subdirectorys  p stamd for parent.if ex  :create directory
mkdir -p new/{list of directorys seperated by ,}}  : will create subdirectorys  p stamd for parent.if ex  :create directory
mkdir -p new/{a,b,c}